data.name: grdInv0110.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT SUNGBUN_CODE, JAERYO_CODE, JAERYO_NAME FROM INV0110 WHERE HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND JAERYO_CODE LIKE :f_jaeryo_code||'%' AND JAERYO_NAME LIKE '%'||:f_jaeryo_name||'%' AND JAERYO_GUBUN IN ('A') AND NVL(BUNRYU1,'N') LIKE :f_bunryu||'%' AND ((:f_bulyong_tp = '1') OR (:f_bulyong_tp = '2' AND BULYONG_DATE IS NULL AND JUKYONG_DATE >= TO_DATE('2008/04/01','YYYY/MM/DD')) OR (:f_bulyong_tp = '3' AND BULYONG_DATE IS NOT NULL)) /******************************************************/ AND NVL(SUNGBUN_CODE,'X') LIKE '%' || :f_sungbun_code || '%' AND NVL(SUNGBUN_NAME,'X') LIKE '%' || :f_sungbun_name || '%' AND NVL(JAERYO_E_NAME,'X') LIKE '%' || :f_jaeryo_e_name || '%' AND NVL(CHANGGO1,'X') LIKE :f_changgo1 || '%' AND NVL(FN_DRG_DRG9992_A32(JAERYO_CODE),'X') LIKE :f_drug_price_code || '%' AND NVL(BUNRYU9 , 'X') LIKE :f_bunryu9 || '%' AND NVL(DRG_TYPE , 'X') LIKE :f_drg_type || '%' AND NVL(SMALL_CODE , 'X') LIKE :f_small_code || '%' AND NVL(BUNRYU3 , 'X') LIKE :f_bunryu3 || '%' AND NVL(SMALL_CODE1 , 'X') LIKE :f_small_code1 || '%' AND NVL(BUNRYU2 , 'X') LIKE :f_bunryu2 || '%' AND NVL(BUNRYU4 , 'X') LIKE :f_bunryu4 || '%' AND NVL(CAUTION_CODE, 'X') LIKE :f_caution_code || '%' AND NVL(BUNRYU5 , '0') LIKE DECODE(NVL(:f_bunryu5,'0'),'0','%',:f_bunryu5) AND NVL(BUNRYU7 , '0') LIKE DECODE(NVL(:f_bunryu7,'0'),'0','%',:f_bunryu7) AND NVL(BUNRYU8 , '0') LIKE DECODE(NVL(:f_bunryu8,'0'),'0','%',:f_bunryu8) AND NVL(BUNRYU6 , '0') LIKE DECODE(NVL(:f_bunryu6,'0'),'0','%',:f_bunryu6) AND ((NVL(:f_yuhyo_to_dt,'X') = 'X') OR (NVL(:f_yuhyo_to_dt,'X') <> 'X' AND NVL(YUHYO_TO_DATE,TO_DATE('30010101','YYYYMMDD')) = TO_DATE(:f_yuhyo_to_dt,'YYYY/MM/DD'))) AND NVL(COMPANY_NAME, 'X') LIKE :f_company_name || '%' AND NVL(CHK1 , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chk1,'N','',:f_chk1) || '%' AND NVL(CHK2 , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chk2,'N','',:f_chk2) || '%' AND NVL(CHK3 , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chk3,'N','',:f_chk3) || '%' AND NVL(CHK4 , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chk4,'N','',:f_chk4) || '%' AND NVL(CHK5 , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chk5,'N','',:f_chk5) || '%' AND NVL(CHK6 , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chk6,'N','',:f_chk6) || '%' AND NVL(CHK7 , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chk7,'N','',:f_chk7) || '%' AND NVL(CHK8 , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chk8,'N','',:f_chk8) || '%' AND NVL(CHK9 , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chk9,'N','',:f_chk9) || '%' AND NVL(CHKA , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chka,'N','',:f_chka) || '%' AND NVL(CHKB , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chkb,'N','',:f_chkb) || '%' AND NVL(CHKC , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chkc,'N','',:f_chkc) || '%' AND NVL(CHKE , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chke,'N','',:f_chke) || '%' AND NVL(CHKF , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chkf,'N','',:f_chkf) || '%' AND NVL(TOIJANG_YN , 'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_toijang_yn,'N','',:f_toijang_yn) || '%' AND NVL(TEXT_COLOR , 'X') LIKE :f_text_color || '%' AND NVL(CUSTOMER_CODE,'X') LIKE :f_customer_code || '%' AND NVL(SUBUL_QCODE_OUT,'X') LIKE :f_subul_qcode_out|| '%' AND NVL(SUBUL_QCODE_INP,'X') LIKE :f_subul_qcode_inp|| '%' AND NVL(SUBUL_QCODE_ER ,'X') LIKE :f_subul_qcode_er || '%' AND NVL(BULYONG_CODE ,'X') LIKE :f_bulyong_code || '%' AND NVL(REMARK ,'X') LIKE '%' || :f_remark || '%' AND NVL(CHKD ,'X') LIKE DECODE(:f_chkd,'N','',:f_chkd) || '%' AND NVL(DRG_COMMENT ,'X') LIKE '%' || :f_drg_comment || '%' AND NVL(DRG_JIBGYE_GUBUN,'0') LIKE DECODE(NVL(:f_drg_jibgye_gubun,'0'),'0','%',:f_drg_jibgye_gubun) AND ((NVL(:f_jukyong_date,'X') = 'X') OR (NVL(:f_jukyong_date,'X') <> 'X' AND NVL(JUKYONG_DATE,TO_DATE('30010101','YYYYMMDD')) = TO_DATE(:f_jukyong_date,'YYYY/MM/DD'))) ORDER BY JAERYO_CODE

data.name: fwkJaeryo.InputSQL
data.value: SELECT JAERYO_CODE, JAERYO_NAME, TO_CHAR(BULYONG_DATE,'YYYY/MM/DD') FROM INV0110 WHERE (JAERYO_CODE LIKE :f_find1||'%' OR JAERYO_NAME LIKE '%'||:f_find1||'%') AND JAERYO_GUBUN = 'A' AND HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code ORDER BY 2
